{"tid":1853023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［實測］口罩豬嘴製作，一個口罩用幾日","createTime":"2020-01-30T17:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T16:09:01.000Z","uid":232450,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2eba4621e76dfc73b547c6accff80d34dac838ec","tid":1853023,"uid":232450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"最近同友人傾開口罩+豬嘴可唔可以將一個口罩分幾日用嘅問題，於是我自己試吓<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">落手整</span></strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：口罩，鉸剪，豬嘴本體，marker，膠紙（唔好學我用過期膠紙），間尺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KW3SCKo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKW3SCKo.png&h=f0318d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n展開口罩，畫出6cm直徑嘅圓形（四條邊唔使剪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LVmv5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LVmv5n.png&h=ca3513e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小心三層口罩散開，可以用膠紙作固定<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PbPnfye.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPbPnfye.png&h=47ac501a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意氣密<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imn8a79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fimn8a79.png&h=fe4ae9c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用Adapter 整起嚟其實更加簡單容易：<br />\n<br />\n4.5 cm直徑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cHMMHfA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcHMMHfA.png&h=cb22cb0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/euMwTn0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeuMwTn0.png&h=5fc04c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意氣密<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eOWdngN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeOWdngN.png&h=d9754754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OVSzRaU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOVSzRaU.png&h=2a36abd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用完記得用酒精/1:49漂白水清潔<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A:<br />\n<br />\nQ: 口罩太濕效果會降低，咁細塊口罩會唔會好易濕？<br />\nA: 豬嘴裏面有瓣膜，呼出嘅空氣唔會接觸到口罩。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 氣密如何？<br />\nA: 我用過期皺紋膠紙都冇問題，用返正常膠紙效果更好<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解唔用P100?<br />\nA: 其實得，不過貴咁解<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解唔隔水蒸？<br />\nA: 會降低口罩密度"},{"pid":"535324c7d6529c721d17e83341f959f10c6fac4d","tid":1853023,"uid":217625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:44:31.000Z","msg":"其實仲有個問題就係好難吸氣"},{"pid":"4e0362e08fdd4f56676212aff694f9d72012cbd9","tid":1853023,"uid":170530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:46:46.000Z","msg":"work wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e4bab2b1c40cd6eb98119f1127caf38a8cdeef","tid":1853023,"uid":226573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:49:00.000Z","msg":"清潔？？"},{"pid":"82a5b2d917f63db65df5bc0c0ac92f54bc993098","tid":1853023,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3e4bab2b1c40cd6eb98119f1127caf38a8cdeef","tid":1853023,"uid":226573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:49:00.000Z","msg":"清潔？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"清潔好麻煩加要用貴酒精？"},{"pid":"7931e89f08243bd463e3d276f9ea95e62e37974b","tid":1853023,"uid":35603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:50:37.000Z","msg":"剪嗰時個口罩都接觸好多空氣中嘅細菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要剪剪貼貼<br />\n不過到冇口罩之時都係一個辦法嚟嘅"},{"pid":"0863c78c1806c68ac7339fced871ea7e1e52dad6","tid":1853023,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:50:52.000Z","msg":"個本體完全消毒好似要用哂成支火酒<br />\n連埋入面 因為要預戴得耐失效之後有菌入去<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"565614bc3fc049ddef56f23e36021bee126efdeb","tid":1853023,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0863c78c1806c68ac7339fced871ea7e1e52dad6","tid